data.description: Stunning, move-in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom rancher located in grand Main Street Landing neighborhood/ central Gloucester. Fall in love with this Grand Bahama floorplan as soon as you step into the foyer. Private Master Suite Split floor plan. The eat-in kitchen features granite counters, stainless steel appliances, a large island, and a pantry. Giant master suite located nearby with a huge walk-in closet, walk-in shower, and dual sinks. Large laundry room and closets. Your living space continues outside with a composite deck overlooking the private, vinyl-fenced backyard and treed privacy beyond. Upgraded luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout living areas, upgraded tile in both bathrooms, oversized attached garage, plenty of storage, and neutral colors throughout. Conveniently located near multiple restaurants, shops, and the beautiful historic Main Street. More photos coming soon. Like Brand New inside. A Must See! Call for private showing....
